definitions.definition: Any animal that undergoes development from an embryo stage with two or three tissue layers, namely the ectoderm , endoderm , and sometimes mesoderm .

main_definition: ( zoology ) Any animal that is multicellular .
secondary_definitions: ( zoology , obsolete ) Any animal that undergoes development from an embryo stage with two or three tissue layers, namely the ectoderm , endoderm , and sometimes mesoderm .
